---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Chert Coin" description="Terms of Service for Chert Coin network, wallet, and related services.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-quantum/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-quantum font-display text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-silver">Last updated: December 7, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="relative pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            By accessing or using the Chert Coin network, wallet, explorer, or any related services ("Services"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, you may not access or use the Services.
          </p>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you and Chert Coin ("we," "us," or "our"). We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Your continued use of the Services following any changes indicates your acceptance of the modified Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">2. Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You must be at least 18 years of age to use the Services. By using the Services, you represent and warrant that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>You are at least 18 years old</li>
            <li>You have the legal capacity to enter into these Terms</li>
            <li>You are not located in, or a citizen or resident of, any jurisdiction where the use of the Services would be illegal or otherwise prohibited</li>
            <li>You will comply with all applicable laws and regulations in your jurisdiction</li>
            <li>You are not subject to economic sanctions or trade restrictions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">3. Nature of Services</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Chert Coin is a decentralized blockchain network. Our Services provide tools and interfaces to interact with this network, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Wallet Services:</strong> Non-custodial wallet software for managing CHERT tokens</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Network Access:</strong> APIs and tools to interact with the Chert blockchain</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Explorer:</strong> Block explorer for viewing network activity</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Staking:</strong> Interfaces for participating in network consensus</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-quantum">Important:</strong> We do not have custody of your private keys, tokens, or any digital assets. You are solely responsible for the security of your wallet and private keys.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">You agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Maintain the security and confidentiality of your private keys and wallet credentials</li>
            <li>Accept full responsibility for all activities that occur under your wallet address</li>
            <li>Not use the Services for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws</li>
            <li>Not attempt to interfere with, compromise, or disrupt the Services or network</li>
            <li>Not use the Services to conduct any fraudulent, deceptive, or manipulative activities</li>
            <li>Not attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble any aspect of the Services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">5. Risks and Disclaimers</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Using blockchain technology and digital assets involves significant risks, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Volatility Risk:</strong> Digital asset prices can be highly volatile</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Technology Risk:</strong> Software may contain bugs or vulnerabilities</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Regulatory Risk:</strong> Laws and regulations may change</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Loss Risk:</strong> Loss of private keys results in permanent loss of assets</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Network Risk:</strong> Network congestion, forks, or failures may occur</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            THE SERVICES ARE PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN NO EVENT SHALL CHERT COIN, ITS AFFILIATES, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, OR AGENTS BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION, LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES, RESULTING FROM:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Your use or inability to use the Services</li>
            <li>Any unauthorized access to or use of our servers or any personal information stored therein</li>
            <li>Any interruption or cessation of transmission to or from the Services</li>
            <li>Any bugs, viruses, or the like that may be transmitted through the Services</li>
            <li>Any loss or damage of any kind incurred as a result of your use of any content posted, transmitted, or otherwise made available via the Services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Chert Coin protocol software is open-source and available under the applicable open-source licenses. However, the Chert Coin name, logo, and branding are proprietary and may not be used without our express written permission.
          </p>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            You retain ownership of any content you create or submit through the Services, but grant us a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, and display such content in connection with the Services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">8. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to the Services at any time, with or without cause, and with or without notice. Upon termination, your right to use the Services will immediately cease.
          </p>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            Due to the decentralized nature of the blockchain, termination of access to our Services does not affect your ability to interact with the Chert blockchain through other means.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which Chert Coin operates, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising under these Terms shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the rules of the applicable arbitration association.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">10. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Email:</strong> legal@chert.network</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Discord:</strong> discord.gg/chert</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">GitHub:</strong> github.com/Silica-Protocol</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    margin-left: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
